com.camerontec.catalys.application.marketdata

Interface IServiceLocator

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IComponent, IHasAttributes, IService
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    StandardServiceLocator

    public interface IServiceLocator
extends IService, IComponent
    Interface required by MarketDataProcessor to locate the market data service to handle specific market data message.

        IMarketDataService findServiceBySymbol(List services,
                                       IFIXMessage message,
                                       String symbol)
        Finds the market data service to handle MarketDataRequest or SecurityStatusRequest message.
        Parameters:
        services - List of market data services.
        message - MarketDataRequest or SecurityStatusRequest message.
        symbol - symbol

        List findServicesByLocatorTags(List services,

        Parameters:
